                      ) AS lead_count,
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l

                      ) AS quotation_count,

                      ) AS proforma_invoice_count,

                      FROM   leads l WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id != 1 AND l.lead_status_id != 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS lead_count,
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l 
                      WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id = 1 AND l.lead_status_id = 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS opportunity_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM quote q 
                      LEFT JOIN quote_product qp ON qp.quote_id = q.quote_id
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = q.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = qp.product_item_id
                      WHERE q.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS quotation_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM proforma_invoice pro_inv 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = pro_inv.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN proforma_invoice_product pip ON pip.proforma_invoice_id = pro_inv.proforma_invoice_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pri ON pri.product_item_id = pip.product_item_id
                      WHERE pro_inv.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS proforma_invoice_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM buyer_order o 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = o.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN buyer_order_product op ON op.buyer_order_id = o.buyer_order_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = op.product_item_id
                      WHERE o.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS order_count

                      ) AS lead_count,
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l 
                      WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id = 1 AND l.lead_status_id = 3  AND l.lead_assigned_to = '4' AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS opportunity_count,

                      LEFT JOIN quote_product qp ON qp.quote_id = q.quote_id
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = q.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = qp.product_item_id
                      WHERE q.status != 2 AND l.lead_assigned_to = '4'  AND STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS quotation_count,

                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = pro_inv.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN proforma_invoice_product pip ON pip.proforma_invoice_id = pro_inv.proforma_invoice_id

                      ) AS proforma_invoice_count,

                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM buyer_order o 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = o.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN buyer_order_product op ON op.buyer_order_id = o.buyer_order_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = op.product_item_id

[2020-09-23 11:02:39] => 103.215.238.22  =>   =>  SELECT  (
                      SELECT COUNT(*)
                      FROM   leads l WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id != 1 AND l.lead_status_id != 3 AND l.lead_assigned_to = '3'  AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS lead_count,
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l 
                      WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id = 1 AND l.lead_status_id = 3  AND l.lead_assigned_to = '3' AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS opportunity_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM quote q 
                      LEFT JOIN quote_product qp ON qp.quote_id = q.quote_id
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = q.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = qp.product_item_id
                      WHERE q.status != 2 AND l.lead_assigned_to = '3'  AND STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS quotation_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM proforma_invoice pro_inv 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = pro_inv.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN proforma_invoice_product pip ON pip.proforma_invoice_id = pro_inv.proforma_invoice_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pri ON pri.product_item_id = pip.product_item_id
                      WHERE pro_inv.status != 2 AND l.lead_assigned_to = '3'  AND STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS proforma_invoice_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM buyer_order o

                      FROM   leads l WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id != 1 AND l.lead_status_id != 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS lead_count,
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l 
                      WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id = 1 AND l.lead_status_id = 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS opportunity_count,

                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM quote q 
                      LEFT JOIN quote_product qp ON qp.quote_id = q.quote_id
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = q.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = qp.product_item_id
                      WHERE q.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS quotation_count,

                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM proforma_invoice pro_inv 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = pro_inv.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN proforma_invoice_product pip ON pip.proforma_invoice_id = pro_inv.proforma_invoice_id

                      ) AS proforma_invoice_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM buyer_order o 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = o.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN buyer_order_product op ON op.buyer_order_id = o.buyer_order_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = op.product_item_id
                      WHERE o.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS order_count

                      ) AS lead_count,
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l 
                      WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id = 1 AND l.lead_status_id = 3  AND l.lead_assigned_to = '4' AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS opportunity_count,

                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM quote q 
                      LEFT JOIN quote_product qp ON qp.quote_id = q.quote_id
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = q.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = qp.product_item_id
                      WHERE q.status != 2 AND l.lead_assigned_to = '4'  AND STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS quotation_count,

                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = pro_inv.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN proforma_invoice_product pip ON pip.proforma_invoice_id = pro_inv.proforma_invoice_id

                      ) AS proforma_invoice_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM buyer_order o 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = o.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN buyer_order_product op ON op.buyer_order_id = o.buyer_order_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = op.product_item_id

[2020-09-23 12:07:55] => 103.215.238.22  =>   =>  SELECT  (
                      SELECT COUNT(*)
                      FROM   leads l WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id != 1 AND l.lead_status_id != 3 AND l.lead_assigned_to = '4'  AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS lead_count,
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l 
                      WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id = 1 AND l.lead_status_id = 3  AND l.lead_assigned_to = '4' AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS opportunity_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM quote q 
                      LEFT JOIN quote_product qp ON qp.quote_id = q.quote_id
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = q.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = qp.product_item_id
                      WHERE q.status != 2 AND l.lead_assigned_to = '4'  AND STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS quotation_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM proforma_invoice pro_inv 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = pro_inv.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN proforma_invoice_product pip ON pip.proforma_invoice_id = pro_inv.proforma_invoice_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pri ON pri.product_item_id = pip.product_item_id
                      WHERE pro_inv.status != 2 AND l.lead_assigned_to = '4'  AND STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS proforma_invoice_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM buyer_order o 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = o.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN buyer_order_product op ON op.buyer_order_id = o.buyer_order_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = op.product_item_id
                      WHERE o.status != 2 AND l.lead_assigned_to = '4'  AND STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS order_count

                      ) AS lead_count,
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l 
                      WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id = 1 AND l.lead_status_id = 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')

                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = q.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = qp.product_item_id
                      WHERE q.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS quotation_count,

                      ) AS proforma_invoice_count,

[2020-09-26 09:50:33] => 103.215.238.22  =>   =>  SELECT  (
                      SELECT COUNT(*)
                      FROM   leads l WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id != 1 AND l.lead_status_id != 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS lead_count,
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l 
                      WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id = 1 AND l.lead_status_id = 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS opportunity_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM quote q 
                      LEFT JOIN quote_product qp ON qp.quote_id = q.quote_id
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = q.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = qp.product_item_id
                      WHERE q.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS quotation_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM proforma_invoice pro_inv 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = pro_inv.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN proforma_invoice_product pip ON pip.proforma_invoice_id = pro_inv.proforma_invoice_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pri ON pri.product_item_id = pip.product_item_id
                      WHERE pro_inv.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS proforma_invoice_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM buyer_order o 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = o.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN buyer_order_product op ON op.buyer_order_id = o.buyer_order_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = op.product_item_id
                      WHERE o.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS order_count

[2020-09-28 09:39:58] => 103.215.238.22  =>   =>  SELECT  (
                      SELECT COUNT(*)
                      FROM   leads l WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id != 1 AND l.lead_status_id != 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS lead_count,
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l 
                      WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id = 1 AND l.lead_status_id = 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS opportunity_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM quote q 
                      LEFT JOIN quote_product qp ON qp.quote_id = q.quote_id
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = q.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = qp.product_item_id
                      WHERE q.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS quotation_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM proforma_invoice pro_inv 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = pro_inv.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN proforma_invoice_product pip ON pip.proforma_invoice_id = pro_inv.proforma_invoice_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pri ON pri.product_item_id = pip.product_item_id
                      WHERE pro_inv.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS proforma_invoice_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM buyer_order o 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = o.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN buyer_order_product op ON op.buyer_order_id = o.buyer_order_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = op.product_item_id
                      WHERE o.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS order_count

                      FROM   leads l WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id != 1 AND l.lead_status_id != 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS lead_count,
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l 
                      WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id = 1 AND l.lead_status_id = 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS opportunity_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM quote q 
                      LEFT JOIN quote_product qp ON qp.quote_id = q.quote_id
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = q.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = qp.product_item_id
                      WHERE q.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS quotation_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM proforma_invoice pro_inv 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = pro_inv.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN proforma_invoice_product pip ON pip.proforma_invoice_id = pro_inv.proforma_invoice_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pri ON pri.product_item_id = pip.product_item_id
                      WHERE pro_inv.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS proforma_invoice_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM buyer_order o 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = o.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN buyer_order_product op ON op.buyer_order_id = o.buyer_order_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = op.product_item_id
                      WHERE o.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS order_count

[2020-09-29 16:09:17] => 103.215.238.22  =>   =>  SELECT  (
                      SELECT COUNT(*)
                      FROM   leads l WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id != 1 AND l.lead_status_id != 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS lead_count,
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l 
                      WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id = 1 AND l.lead_status_id = 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS opportunity_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM quote q 
                      LEFT JOIN quote_product qp ON qp.quote_id = q.quote_id
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = q.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = qp.product_item_id
                      WHERE q.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS quotation_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM proforma_invoice pro_inv 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = pro_inv.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN proforma_invoice_product pip ON pip.proforma_invoice_id = pro_inv.proforma_invoice_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pri ON pri.product_item_id = pip.product_item_id
                      WHERE pro_inv.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS proforma_invoice_count,

                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = op.product_item_id
                      WHERE o.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS order_count

                      FROM   leads l WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id != 1 AND l.lead_status_id != 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS lead_count,
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l 
                      WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id = 1 AND l.lead_status_id = 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')

                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM quote q 
                      LEFT JOIN quote_product qp ON qp.quote_id = q.quote_id
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = q.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = qp.product_item_id
                      WHERE q.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS quotation_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM proforma_invoice pro_inv 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = pro_inv.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN proforma_invoice_product pip ON pip.proforma_invoice_id = pro_inv.proforma_invoice_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pri ON pri.product_item_id = pip.product_item_id
                      WHERE pro_inv.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS proforma_invoice_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM buyer_order o 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = o.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN buyer_order_product op ON op.buyer_order_id = o.buyer_order_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = op.product_item_id
                      WHERE o.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')

[2020-09-30 10:00:50] => 103.215.238.22  =>   =>  SELECT  (
                      SELECT COUNT(*)
                      FROM   leads l WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id != 1 AND l.lead_status_id != 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS lead_count,
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l 
                      WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id = 1 AND l.lead_status_id = 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS opportunity_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM quote q 
                      LEFT JOIN quote_product qp ON qp.quote_id = q.quote_id
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = q.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = qp.product_item_id
                      WHERE q.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS quotation_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM proforma_invoice pro_inv 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = pro_inv.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN proforma_invoice_product pip ON pip.proforma_invoice_id = pro_inv.proforma_invoice_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pri ON pri.product_item_id = pip.product_item_id
                      WHERE pro_inv.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS proforma_invoice_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM buyer_order o 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = o.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN buyer_order_product op ON op.buyer_order_id = o.buyer_order_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = op.product_item_id
                      WHERE o.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS order_count
                  FROM DUAL  =>  0.00111

                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = q.lead_id

                      ) AS quotation_count,

[2020-10-02 15:30:13] => 103.215.238.22  =>   =>  SELECT  (
                      SELECT COUNT(*)
                      FROM   leads l WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id != 1 AND l.lead_status_id != 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS lead_count,
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l 
                      WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id = 1 AND l.lead_status_id = 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS opportunity_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM quote q 
                      LEFT JOIN quote_product qp ON qp.quote_id = q.quote_id
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = q.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = qp.product_item_id
                      WHERE q.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS quotation_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM proforma_invoice pro_inv 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = pro_inv.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN proforma_invoice_product pip ON pip.proforma_invoice_id = pro_inv.proforma_invoice_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pri ON pri.product_item_id = pip.product_item_id

                      ) AS proforma_invoice_count,
                      
                      (

                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = o.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN buyer_order_product op ON op.buyer_order_id = o.buyer_order_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = op.product_item_id
                      WHERE o.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')

[2020-10-02 17:21:15] => 103.215.238.22  =>   =>  SELECT lf.*,cb.lead_name,p.product_name,u.name,ac.name AS country_name FROM lead_followups lf 
                            LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = lf.lead_id
                            LEFT JOIN contact_book cb ON cb.contact_book_id = l.contact_book_id
                            LEFT JOIN ad_countries ac ON ac.id = cb.country

[2020-10-05 10:03:59] => 14.102.45.21  =>   =>  SELECT  (
                      SELECT COUNT(*)
                      FROM   leads l WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id != 1 AND l.lead_status_id != 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS lead_count,
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l 
                      WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id = 1 AND l.lead_status_id = 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS opportunity_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM quote q 
                      LEFT JOIN quote_product qp ON qp.quote_id = q.quote_id
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = q.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = qp.product_item_id
                      WHERE q.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS quotation_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM proforma_invoice pro_inv 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = pro_inv.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN proforma_invoice_product pip ON pip.proforma_invoice_id = pro_inv.proforma_invoice_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pri ON pri.product_item_id = pip.product_item_id
                      WHERE pro_inv.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS proforma_invoice_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM buyer_order o 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = o.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN buyer_order_product op ON op.buyer_order_id = o.buyer_order_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = op.product_item_id
                      WHERE o.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2020-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2021-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS order_count
                  FROM DUAL  =>  0.00198
[2020-10-05 10:03:59] => 14.102.45.21  =>   =>  SELECT COUNT(bop.product_item_id) AS product_order_count,p.product_name,p.product_id FROM buyer_order_product bop

          LEFT JOIN products p ON p.product_id = pi.product_id
